 it's gonna actually change the thing.

00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:36.900
 So let, so you see I'm trying to show

00:13:36.900 --> 00:13:39.940
 all the possible error checking that can happen.

00:13:39.940 --> 00:13:42.420
 So let's go ahead and without further ado,

